BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:V2F84ldowzzp8AHeEfPJh
SUMMARY:Get Your Sphere in Gear w/ Liz Johnson- Lunch & Learn
DTSTAMP:20260214T003547Z
DTSTART:20260218T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Learn how to turn your sphere of influence into a powerful refe
	rral engine with proven real estate strategies.\n\nTHIS CLASS IS FREE FOR 
	KELLER WILLIAMS BOTHELL AGENTS. PLEASE CHECK YOUR EMAIL FOR AN ACCESS CODE
	.  \n\nGet Your Sphere In Gear is a practical\, high-impact real estate tr
	aining designed for agents who want to generate more referrals\, strengthe
	n client relationships\, and build a sustainable business through their sp
	here of influence. \n\nIn this engaging session\, you’ll learn how to move
	 beyond passive networking and implement a proactive\, relationship-driven
	 approach to staying top-of-mind with past clients\, current contacts\, an
	d future prospects. Through proven real estate referral and marketing stra
	tegies\, you’ll discover effective methods for outreach\, follow-up\, and 
	consistent touchpoints that transform everyday conversations into real bus
	iness opportunities. \n\nWhether you’re a new agent building your database
	 or an experienced professional looking to increase referrals\, this class
	 delivers actionable tools\, systems\, and best practices you can implemen
	t immediately to grow your network and drive long-term business success. \
	n\nThe class is led by Liz Johnson\, a seasoned real estate professional b
	ased in Washington State with over 1\,500 closed transactions since 2004. 
	A proud U.S. Army veteran\, Liz brings a disciplined\, mission-driven mind
	set to her business\, which thrives almost entirely on referrals from frie
	nds\, family\, and past clients. She is the author of Perk Your Sphere and
	 her newest book\, Get Your Sphere in Gear\, and is widely known for her e
	xpertise in relationship-based business\, problem-solving\, and navigating
	 complex transactions with confidence and care. \n\nIf you’re ready to sto
	p leaving referrals to chance and start working your sphere with intention
	\, this class is for you.
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/get-your-sphere-in-gear-w
	-liz-johnson-lunch-learn/18079675/2026-02-18T00
LOCATION:Keller Williams Realty Bothell\, 22614 Bothell Everett HWY\, Bothe
	ll\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
