DTSTAMP:20260214T003547Z
DTSTART:20260227T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Description Unwind at the end of the month or spend your lunch 
	break in community at Minority Veterans of America's Quiet Reading Club. T
	his drop-in\, drop-out gathering offers a calm\, shared space to read toge
	ther in silence-no pressure to socialize\, just the comfort of being along
	side others. Bring whatever you're reading \\(or choose from our Little Fr
	ee Library\\)\, build a sandwich from our lunch bar\, and settle into a co
	zy spot. Presence is enough\, conversation is optional\, and the shared qu
	iet creates connection.All are welcome\, including veterans\, active-duty\
	, military family members\, and allies. Lunhc will be available\, free par
	king.
